OL,5, Forty years on, a former coal miner on 
OL,6, the front line in the 1984-85 miners'  
OL,7, strike reveals the painful choice he   
OL,8, had to make when he lost his newborn   
OL,9, son during what was arguably the UK's  
OL,10, most bitter industrial dispute.        
OL,12,F"I've got a story to tell, and I think 
OL,13,Fit's important that some people hear   
OL,14,Fit," says Dave Roper.                  
